description: The web animation API programmatically creates, inspects, and controls element animations, to change and synchronize appearance over time.
description_html: The web animation API programmatically creates, inspects, and controls element animations, to change and synchronize appearance over time.
name: Web animations

firefox.notes: Before version 59, the pending status was reported by a "pending" value returned from Animation.playState.

firefox_android.notes: Before version 59, the pending status was reported by a "pending" value returned from Animation.playState.

chrome.notes: Before Chrome 50/Opera 37, this property returned idle for an animation that had not yet started. Starting with Chrome 50/Opera 37, it shows paused.

chrome_android.notes: Before Chrome Android 50/Opera 37, this property returned idle for an animation that had not yet started. Starting with Chrome Android 50/Opera 37, it shows paused.

firefox.notes: Before Firefox 59, this property returned pending for Animations with incomplete asynchronous operations but as of Firefox 59 this is indicated by the separate Animation.pending property. This reflects recent changes to the specification.

firefox_android.notes: Before Firefox for Android 59, this property returned pending for Animations with incomplete asynchronous operations but as of Firefox for Android 59 this is indicated by the separate Animation.pending property. This reflects recent changes to the specification.

oculus.notes: Before Quest Browser 5.0/Opera 37, this property returned idle for an animation that had not yet started. Starting with Quest Browser 5.0/Opera 37, it shows paused.

opera.notes: Before Chrome 50/Opera 37, this property returned idle for an animation that had not yet started. Starting with Chrome 50/Opera 37, it shows paused.

opera_android.notes: Before Chrome 50/Opera 37, this property returned idle for an animation that had not yet started. Starting with Chrome 50/Opera 37, it shows paused.

samsunginternet_android.notes: Before Samsung Internet 5.0/Opera 37, this property returned idle for an animation that had not yet started. Starting with Samsung Internet 5.0/Opera 37, it shows paused.

webview_android.notes: Before WebView Android 50/Opera 37, this property returned idle for an animation that had not yet started. Starting with WebView Android 50/Opera 37, it shows paused.
